The paper discusses the construction and analysis of network structures, which is a common topic in several sub-categories of computer science. Specifically, the paper covers methods for inferring network structures from data, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), statistical learning (cs.SD), machine learning (cs.LG), databases (cs.DB), and systems and control (cs.SY).
